                "invention-title": [
                    "Industrial waste heat hydrogen and oxygen production integrated device and application thereof",
                    "一种工业余热制氢和氧综合装置及其应用"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The industrial waste heat hydrogen and oxygen production comprehensive device comprises a waste heat recovery system and a thermochemical circulation hydrogen and oxygen production system, one end of the waste heat recovery system is connected to a waste heat pipeline of a factory, the other end of the waste heat recovery system is divided into two pipelines, one pipeline is directly connected to a steam pipeline of the factory, and the other pipeline is directly connected to a steam pipeline of the factory. One waste heat recovery system is connected to the rear part of the waste heat recovery system, the other waste heat recovery system is connected to the rear part of the thermal chemical cycle hydrogen and oxygen production system, steam is fed into the system to produce hydrogen and oxygen, and the waste heat recovery system is controlled by the control system. The industrial waste heat is utilized through the thermal chemical cycle hydrogen production technology, and particularly, a large amount of low-grade waste heat which is difficult to utilize at present can be utilized to produce hydrogen; and meanwhile, the obtained hydrogen can be supplied as a factory production raw material or energy on the spot, so that the consumption and carbon emission of factory fossil energy are reduced, and the green and low-carbon transformation of the factory is guaranteed."
                },
                {
                    "p": "一种工业余热制氢和氧综合装置及其应用，其中装置包括余热回收系统和热化学循环制氢制氧系统，所述余热回收系统的一端连接至工厂的余热管道，另一端分成两条管路，一条直接连接至工厂的蒸汽管线，另一条连接至后方的热化学循环制氢制氧系统，将蒸汽送入至系统中制成氢气和氧气，该余热回收系统由控制系统控制，本发明通过热化学循环制氢技术利用工业余热，尤其是可大量利用目前难以利用的低品位余热制氢，实现氢能绿色、零碳生产，同时所得氢气可就地作为工厂生产原料或能源供给，减少工厂化石能源的消耗及碳排放，保障工厂向绿色低碳转型。"
                }
            ]
